# Commit authorship

- Author and committer must always be: Digvijay Waghela `<digvijay.vaghela@yahoo.com>`
- Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Made-with: Cursor`, `--trailer`, or any Cursor/agent attribution to commits or PRs
- If the environment injects a Cursor trailer, amend immediately to remove it before pushing
- Prefer `GIT_AUTHOR_*` / `GIT_COMMITTER_*` env vars for identity; do not change global git config unless the user asks
